Detailed Description

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum Vps_VipAncChSel8b

It gives the imformation in 8b interface mode from where to extract Vertical Ancillary data.

Enumerator
VPS_VIP_ANC_CH_SEL_8B_LUMA_SIDE 

Extract 8b Mode Vertical Ancillary Data from Luma Sites.

VPS_VIP_ANC_CH_SEL_8B_CHROMA_SIDE 

Extract 8b Mode Vertical Ancillary Data from Chroma Sites.

VPS_VIP_ANC_CH_SEL_DONT_CARE 

Value is dont care.

enum Vps_VipCtrlChanSel

Enum for Control Channel Selection.

It describes channels numbers from extract control code and Vertical Ancillary Data.

Enumerator
VPS_VIP_CTRL_CHAN_SEL_7_0 

Use data[7:0] to extract control codes.

VPS_VIP_CTRL_CHAN_SEL_15_8 

Use data[15:8] to extract control codes.

VPS_VIP_CTRL_CHAN_SEL_23_16 

Use data[23:16] to extract control codes.

VPS_VIP_CTRL_CHAN_DONT_CARE 

Value is dont care.

enum Vps_VipFidDetectMode

It is only used for Discrete Sync.

Enumerator
VPS_VIP_FID_DETECT_MODE_PIN 

Take FID from pin.

VPS_VIP_FID_DETECT_MODE_VSYNC 

FID is determined by VSYNC skew.

VPS_VIP_FID_DETECT_MODE_DONT_CARE 

Value is dont care.

enum Vps_VipLineCaptureStyle

It is used only for Discrete Sync.

Enumerator
VPS_VIP_LINE_CAPTURE_STYLE_HSYNC 

Use HSYNC style line capture.

VPS_VIP_LINE_CAPTURE_STYLE_AVID 

Use AVID style line capture.

VPS_VIP_LINE_CAPTURE_STYLE_DONT_CARE 

Value is dont care.

enum Vps_VipRepackMode

Different Repacker Modes supported by VIP Port A For first 6 modes: Enum names assume C=[23:16], B=[15:8], A=[7:0] Enum name is of format VPS_VIP_<repacker INPUT>_TO_<repacker OUTPUT> For VPS_VIP_REPACK_RAW16_TO_RGB565: OUT[23:16]=IN[15:11]['b000] OUT[15: 8]=IN[10: 5]['b00] OUT[ 7: 0]=IN[ 4: 0]['b000] For VPS_VIP_REPACK_RAW12_SWAP: OUT[23:12] = IN[11:0], OUT[11:0] = IN[23:12],.

enum Vps_VipRepackMode

enum Vps_VipSrcNumPos

In embedded sync for 2x/4x mux mode there are two way to extract soruce number, one is from least significant nibble of the XV/fvh codeword and other is least significant nibble of a horizontal blanking pixel value.

Enumerator
VPS_VIP_SRC_NUM_POS_LS_NIBBLE_OF_CODEWORD 

srcnum is in the least significant nibble of the XV/fvh codeword.

VPS_VIP_SRC_NUM_POS_LS_NIBBLE_OF_HOR_BLNK_PIX 

srcnum is in the least significant nibble of a horizontal blanking pixelvalue.

VPS_VIP_SRC_NUM_POS_DONT_CARE 

Value is dont care.

enum Vps_VipSyncType

Enum for Vip Sync Type.

enum Vps_VipParserSyncType.

Enumerator
VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_SINGLE_422_YUV 

Embedded sync single 4:2:2 YUV stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_2X_422_YUV 

Embedded sync 2x multiplexed 4:2:2 YUV stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_4X_422_YUV 

Embedded sync 4x multiplexed 4:2:2 YUV stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_LINE_YUV 

Embedded sync line multiplexed 4:2:2 YUV stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_DIS_SINGLE_YUV 

Discrete sync single 4:2:2 YUV stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_SINGLE_RGB_OR_444_YUV 

Embedded sync single RGB stream or single 444 YUV stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_2X_RGB 

Embedded sync 2x multiplexed RGB stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_4X_RGB 

Embedded sync 4x multiplexed RGB stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_EMB_LINE_RGB 

Embedded sync line multiplexed RGB stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_DIS_SINGLE_8B_RGB 

Discrete sync single 8b RGB stream.

VPS_VIP_SYNC_TYPE_DIS_SINGLE_24B_RGB 

Discrete sync single 24b RGB stream.
